[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "は～、暇ねぇ……遊ぼうにも、\n見渡す限り山しかないし",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_00712",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "いいじゃない。綺麗な湧き水に、美味しい空気。\n休むには最適な場所よ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00713",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "よく言えば田舎、悪く言っても田舎……\nそういう所だよね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00714",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "いいじゃないか。田舎で結構。\nレスナたちの故郷を悪く言うもんじゃないよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00715",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "でも、退屈なのは確かかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00716",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "我々はともかく、多くの人間は\n肉体と精神の疲労を癒す時間が必要",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_00717",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "キューンは、だいぶ元気になった。\nようやく不平不満を口にしてくれるように……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_00718",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "まさか、愚痴ってほめられるなんて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00719",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "まあ、確かにはたから見てると、\n長男長女に脅されて従ってた末っ子ではある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_00720",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "猫被ってるんだよ。\n普段は結構甘えん坊だからね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00721",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "えー、そっかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00722",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "はは、ゴゥやヤドヴィガには甘やかされてたからね。\nでも、今回の戦いで一皮むけた気がするよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_037_00723",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "確かに。限界近く……もしかしたら限界以上に\n力と勇気を引き出して頑張ってたかも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00724",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "そっかな、えへへ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00725",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "といっても、もうヘルト兄貴やゼロ姉貴に逆らうのは\n怖すぎるからやりたくないけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00726",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "まったくね。今回はたまたま助かったけど、\n命がいくつあっても足りないよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00727",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "そういうわりには、スカッとした顔してるけどね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_00728",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "そりゃまあ暴君に一発反撃できたんだから、\nそこはすっきりしたけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_037_00729",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "あはは……\n今後の仕返しが怖いから、私はつくづく小物かも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00730",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "そんな私が勇気を出せたのはね、\nヴァレリア姉ちゃんがいたからだよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00731",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "え、私？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00732",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "うん。ヴァレリア姉ちゃんが頑張ってる姿を\n見てたから、自分も頑張ろうって思えたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00733",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "頑張りなら、それこそアルビーナとか\nクレオなんかも頑張ってたと思うけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00734",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ううん。記憶を失っても、お姉ちゃんはやっぱり\nお姉ちゃんだった。かっこよかったよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_037_00735",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "諾。背中を見て、ついていけば間違いない。\nそう思える安心感があった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_037_00736",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "い、いやー、そう面と向かって言われると、\nなんか、恥ずかしいわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00737",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ハイディ",
		"romanized_name": "Heidi",
		"model_path_hash": "4131218363577277631",
		"text": "よかったじゃん。ちゃんとお姉ちゃん、\nやれてるってよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_051_037_00738",
		"still_path_hash": "5092952616707211512",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "いたたっ、強く叩きすぎだって！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_037_00739",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]